An eight-year-old girl drowned in Uitenhage on Saturday afternoon An eight-year-old girl, swimming with friends, drowned at a Willow Dam offspring in Uitenhage on Saturday afternoon (11/03/17). The girl, who was swimming with four friends, drowned a little after 2pm. Emergency services, who were on the scene, recovered the body after the 10111 call centre had been alerted to the tragedy. Related Share on Facebook Share Share on Twitter Tweet Share on Google Plus Share